-- BNP Paribas Hires Fittipaldi From Standard for Latin America Debt Markets
-- Veronica Navarro Espinosa
-- 2010-06-14T15:17:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/bnp-paribas-hires-fittipaldi-from-standard-for-latin-america-debt-markets.html

          
          
             BNP Paribas, France’s largest bank,
has hired  Rodrigo Fittipaldi  from Standard Bank Group Ltd. to
bolster its Latin American bond sale business.  
 Fittipaldi will join BNP Paribas’s debt capital markets
group in Sao Paulo, according to an internal memo obtained by
Bloomberg News. BNP Paribas also hired  Jose Munhoz  and  Jose Guimaro  to work in its Brazil institutional fixed-income sales
group in Sao Paulo.  
 Edwina Frawley-Gangahar , a spokeswoman with the bank in New
York, confirmed the hirings.  
